         MACRO                                                          00160000
.*                                                                      00170000
.* Structured programming macro: CASE                                   00180000
.* Combines with ELSE and ENDCASE to conditionally execute code-blocks  00190000
.*                                                                      00200000
&LABEL   CASE  &NEST=NO                * YES to force nesting           00210000
.*                                     * Condition in &SYSLIST          00220000
.********************************************************************** 00221001
.*                                                                      00222001
.*       IMPORTANT NOTICE                                               00223001
.*       ========= ======                                               00224001
.*                                                                      00225001
